      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Defra launches the Healthy Bees Plan 2030 to help protect honey bees
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Honey bees contribute directly to local food production and make an important contribution, through pollination, to crop production and the wider environment. </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 3 November 2020
</div>

      <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata__other">
        <dl data-module="track-click">
            <dt class="app-c-publisher-metadata__term">
              From:
            </dt>
